    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You magically animate either a large object or a group of smaller objects, which begin floating in the air.</em></p><p><strong>Summoning Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Both Objects</strong></p><ul><li><p>Are &amp;reference[construct]{constructs} and act immediately after the end of your turns. The objects follow your commands, otherwise only defending themselves from attackers.</p></li><li><p>Are immune to &amp;reference[poison]{poison} and &amp;reference[psychic]{psychic} damage, and immune to the &amp;reference[paralyzed]{paralyzed}, &amp;reference[poisoned]{poisoned}, &amp;reference[prone]{prone}, &amp;reference[unconscious], and &amp;reference[exhaustion]{exhaustion} conditions.</p></li><li><p>Have &amp;reference[blindsight] within 60 ft. and are blind beyond that radius.</p></li><li><p>Have a flying speed of 30 ft.</p></li><li><p>Have a melee attack they can use on their turn:</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Melee Attack </strong>- 1 Creature (5 ft.)</p><ul><li><p><strong>Attack Bonus:</strong> +8</p></li><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> [[/damage 2d10 + 4 bludgeoning]] damage.*</p></li></ul></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><p><strong>Large Object</strong></p><ul><li><p>It is a large &amp;reference[construct]{construct}.</p></li><li><p>It can carry medium or smaller creatures like a mount or vehicle.</p></li><li><p>It has AC 15, 60 hit points,* and all its ability scores are 2, except &amp;reference[strength]{strength}, which is 18, &amp;reference[constitution]{constitution}, which is 14, and &amp;reference[dexterity]{dexterity} which is 10.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Large Swarm of Objects</strong></p><ul><li><p>It is a swarm of tiny and/or small &amp;reference[construct]{constructs}.</p></li><li><p>As a swarm, it has resistance to all damage meant to damage a single creature, and vulnerability to area of effect damage. It also have the standard @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-creature-features.Item.WpPWeLaBqUVj2mlj]{swarm features}.</p></li><li><p>It has AC 15, 40 hit points,* and all its ability scores are 2, except &amp;reference[dexterity]{dexterity}, which is 18, &amp;reference[constitution]{constitution}, which is 14, and &amp;reference[strength]{strength} which is 10.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The object(s)'s damage increases by [[/r 1d10 fire]]{1d10} for each spell level above 5th level. For each spell level above 5th level, it also gains more hit points: 15 hit points for large objects and 10 hit points for swarms.</p><p></p><p><em>An object might be animated but start &amp;reference[grappled] or &amp;reference[restrained] if fastened to something or part of something larger.</em></p>",
